{"tid":2106452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國男子參加新冠派對後染疫亡　臨終前承認自己犯錯","createTime":"2020-07-13T10:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:35:58.000Z","uid":66324,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"165039da6badbd645d0669f4932a1164b804ba14","tid":2106452,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:47:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397794&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=41aa517f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397794&h=b6f87dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397794</a><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n美國得州聖安東尼奧一個30歲男子參加一個「新冠派對」，即是與確診者一起聚會測試病毒是否能傳染別人，或試圖做到群體免疫，結果這個男子「中招」死亡，他臨終前才知後悔莫及。<br />\n<br />\n她指當地新冠病毒檢測，結果呈陽性的比率數星期內由5%急升至22%，患者的年齡層亦擴大，不少只有二、三十歲，求診時病徵輕微，但病情急速惡化，部分人情況危殆，她希望大眾正視疫情。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，亞拉巴馬州有大學生賭誰在聚會後首先染疫，並設有獎金。有醫生批評「新冠派對」危險、不負責任和可能致命，警告即使感染後不一定等於免疫，也可以「復陽」。"},{"pid":"2208bcdc4da41320d8d27100a67e78a3056326cb","tid":2106452,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"470b4a549883e938e5bdef2a3079e6027d0468e1","tid":2106452,"uid":158336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e26d322f38037759390150561b1c4873e0c29","tid":2106452,"uid":275475,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"陳雲美國弟子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602b5714df02f16096a7d10796a0bc3931769947","tid":210645